title: For Sale/Trade:  Used guns for sale.
postcontent:
Ok people I am tired of seeing these used gun listing prices for new prices or even higher. The only reason that this is happening is because buyers don't know what they are doing. Go online and look for what the gun is going for new at a few sights before you come here and look at used ones. Its like buying a car. Why would you pay them same price for a car with miles that you can go somewhere and get one brand new? That is insane. Also just because it says "New" or "LNIB" doesn't mean anything. If it is not a licensed dealer selling the gun the gun is USED!!!!

Do your homework, look at brand name sites, gun auction sites, forums, or even go to an actual gun shop and see other prices. Maybe if gun buyers get a little smarter then gun seller can stop trying to rip all of us off.
